Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:17.13,main,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:18.76,main,,0,0,0,,教皇圣下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:26.09,main,,0,0,0,,圣下被...
