Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:36.61,main,,0,0,0,,全体撒退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:46.99,main,,0,0,0,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:48.16,main,,0,0,0,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:49.95,main,,0,0,0,,这样可不行 振作点
